{"tid":2260491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年10月27日：面對支那三連攻勢，香港人，你肯放棄香港未？","createTime":"2020-10-27T15:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T06:01:37.000Z","uid":131691,"like":143,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"b6117fba86ec78d5565051fab00fa01c56bc68e6","tid":2260491,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"1. 學生動源被捕<br />\n2. 「健康」監控碼<br />\n3. 共產黨員持證攻入香港大學<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">「聽日繼續返工」「輸了」「放棄啦」<br />\n「抵死」「美國唔會幫你」「人哋利用你㗎咋弱智仔」<br />\n「世界都已經放棄咗香港，你仲好撚鍾意香港只係嘥時間」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dn2vdNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdn2vdNr.png&h=87ebb043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>你會爲支那甘願放棄香港嗎？</em>  </p><br />\n<br />\n<strong><p class=\"center\">敵人只會繼續進攻，<br />\n前路只會更加黑暗，<br />\n但係香港人永遠唔會放棄香港，<br />\n因爲香港係屬於香港人，<br />\n因爲香港係香港人與生俱來嘅領土，<br />\n因爲香港唔係屬於英國，更加唔係屬於支那，<br />\n因爲香港係屬於我哋每一位。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">Resist the demoralisation<br />\nRemember the captured and the fallen<br />\nRevenge no matter the cost</span></p></strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htE9us7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtE9us7.gif&h=5404ec4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"1ebe8f380ce64fc1289021696846ca6081c226c5","tid":2260491,"uid":77717,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"認真，可以點反擊"},{"pid":"f1f35ea71bc0e818c46f04ba4bacf7f67281a78b","tid":2260491,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"美國咪幫咗囉<br />\n仲可以有人講呢句廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c207264d38caeb480f5e091cd565f386d7e2d1","tid":2260491,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.